creator: TaskEasy, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Download TaskEasy for Contractors, the app created for the landscaping and lawn mowing professionals to grow the business and simplify life of the small local business owners.

Being a TaskEasy Contractor is an easy way to bring more customers and get lawn care jobs without any additional costs.

2 MILLION LAWNS MOWED IN 50 STATES AND COUNTING
We work with businesses, real estate portfolio owners, homeowners, and renters all across the country.

ONE EASY APP
Accept new lawn care jobs in your area, get paid, manage your crew, view routes and work schedules, all in one easy and intuitive app.

HOW IT WORKS:

1. Apply

Fill out our application at www.taskeasy.com/contractors and give us some basic info about your business.

2. Get Offers

We'll contact you when there are new properties that need service in your area.

3. Get Jobs

Build and expand routes with TaskEasy properties.
descriptionShort: TaskEasy App for contractors to manage services work directly from their phone.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We are continuously making improvements and bug fixes to the app.

Please make sure to have the latest version of the app to enjoy the most recent features
